==Documentation==
This template creates a region page layout.
Uses Semantic MediaWiki for structured data storage and display.

Regions represent geographic territories for game releases (e.g., North America, Europe, Japan).

===Parameters===
{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Parameter !! Description
|-
|| Name || Display name of the region
|-
|| Guid || Giant Bomb API identifier
|-
|| Abbreviation || Short code (e.g., NA, EU, JP)
|-
|| Image || Region image/flag
|-
|| Deck || Short description
|}

===Usage===
<pre>
{{Region
| Name = North America
| Guid = 3075-1
| Abbreviation = NA
| Deck = Includes the United States, Canada, and Mexico...
}}

== Overview ==
Your wiki content here...

{{RegionEnd}}
</pre>
